name: SpacePhotos

skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: space photos
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Explore the universe with Space Photos.
Get the best astronomical and space mission photos in your Alexa app, and listen to their explanations.
By saying “Send me a photo”, you will receive a card in your Alexa app containing the explanation of the photo and a web address to download it.
The web address is valid for one download only.
To display photos on the screen, the device must support APL (Alexa Presentation Language) version 1.1 or higher.
